        <content type="html" xml:base="https://salif.github.io/zola-themes-collection/demo/edge/blog/development-workflow-automation/">&lt;p&gt;A well-automated development workflow can save hours of repetitive work and reduce human error. Hereâ€™s how to set up automation that actually makes your life easier.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;git-hooks-for-quality-control&quot;&gt;Git Hooks for Quality Control&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Git hooks run automatically at certain points in the Git workflow:&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;pre-commit-hook&quot;&gt;Pre-commit Hook&lt;&#x2F;h3&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;bash&quot; style=&quot;background-color:#151515;color:#e8e8d3;&quot; class=&quot;language-bash &quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#888888;&quot;&gt;#!&#x2F;bin&#x2F;sh
